OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry day with long sunny
OL,6,Fspells, although some cloud will
OL,7,Fbubble up over Shetland during the
OL,8,Fafternoon. A cool start to the day but
OL,9,Ffeeling quite warm in the afternoon
OL,10,Fsunshine with light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA bright evening then
OL,13,Fremaining dry overnight with long
OL,14,Fclear spells. More cloud at times
OL,15,Facross Shetland. Becoming rather cool
OL,16,Fovernight.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FAnother dry day with variable
OL,19,Famounts of cloud and some decent
OL,20,Fspells of sunshine. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
