OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FHigh
OL,6,Fpressure will maintain the dry and
OL,7,Fsettled weather through this period.
OL,8,FRather cool and cloudy at times but
OL,9,Fsome bright spells too.
